title: #92Noon! 9a Hour 9/19 - Nordo in for PA!  PA from Phily, Comeback Kids, Dave Sinykin
description: PA calls in from Philly to preview the Monday Night Football matchup between the Vikings & Eagles, Nordo recaps all of the crazy comebacks from around the NFL, & Dave Sinykin joins the show to discuss the Packers bounce back game against the Bears.
